content.rendered:
Directed by Swaroop Rsj

Written by Swaroop Rsj

Star Jay Chandra (Police officer). Johnson D M (Kidnapper). Jayateertha. Viswanath Mandalika ((as Viswanath)). Taapsee Pannu. Hareesh Peradi (Ram Shetty). Kishore Kumar Polimera (Raghava’s Father). Bhannu Prakshan (Raghava). Satyam Rajesh. Rangadham (Ragupathi father). Harsh Roshan (Raghupathi). Phva Sanjeevi (Gundu Uncle-Bike Guy). Rishab Shetty (Khalil). Manikanta Varanasi (Lorry Driver). Harsha Vardhan. Vikram Veramaneni. Ravindra Vijay (Vikram)

Language Telugu

Producers N.M. Pasha. Anvesh Reddy. Niranjan Reddy

Production Matinee Entertainments
